Name: SEX with HITLER: WW2
About the game: Sex With Hitler:WW2 is an action-packed top-down shooter set in the midst of World War 2. You take on the role of a Hitler fighting against the enemy powers, battling through the ruins of cities and the trenches of war-torn landscapes. With a variety of weapons at your disposal, including rifles, machine guns, and grenades, you must take on enemy troops, tanks, and planes, as you strive to complete missions and achieve victory. As you progress through the game, you can earn upgrades for your weapons and abilities, allowing you to take on tougher challenges and become a more effective soldier. This game provides endless hours of action-packed fun for gamers of all skill levels. Features: Intense top-down shooter gameplay set in a WW2 setting. Variety of weapons including rifles, machine guns, and grenades. Realistic environments ranging from war-torn cities to battlefields. Challenging missions against enemy troops, tanks, and planes. Upgrades for weapons and abilities to improve your soldier. Campaign mode for a story-driven single-player experience. Realistic sound effects and music to enhance the immersive experience. Historical accuracy in terms of weapons, equipment, and settings to provide an authentic WW2 experience All characters are over 18 years old
